{"tid":151270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子被獵精黨擄走　遭4女輪流性侵強取精液","createTime":"2017-03-10T16:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T01:07:05.000Z","uid":82186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66aab8dcea8ed2bef4e0cc3b9a6d7a06b820f0f9","tid":151270,"uid":82186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"南非內陸國家辛巴威（Republic of Zimbabwe），又出現「女子獵精黨」，一位20歲男教師被4名女子擄走，強迫多次性交、採精，結束後被全裸丟在樹叢裡。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，目擊者指出，「司機突然停下來，其中一個女子迅速矇住被害人眼睛，其他人則是協力把他手腳綁起來」。警方表示，被害者說他被強迫喝下一種不明液體後就昏過去，並懷疑被那票人輪流性侵採精，之後被丟到路旁後才得以脫身報警，並到醫院驗傷。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n男子被獵精並不是當地首次發生的案件，2011年開始，便陸續有相關案例發生，當時警方曾逮捕3名男子，並取出31個裝滿精液的保險套。去年2月也有男子被獵精，受害男子表示，「一名女子有用保險套，其餘兩人沒有安全措施就與我性交，她們取得精液後就把我丟了」。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n當地傳統文化相信男性的精液會帶來好運，且會用精液來行巫術，因此精液在當地有市場，也有行情，而精液的「行情價」是250毫升30美元(約新台幣900元)。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9385effadfbe0538112a35375833b24c3dc2cf","tid":151270,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"活採<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30a381c2ab1e1b7bbc21fa652c0e9edd9118f1e","tid":151270,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"640eea46ae1d303953b31aeafd297620cc828441","tid":151270,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"唔合理<br />\n點解唔去做雞呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ced7ad07da8879c8c4ce5d93fc89b8b0b0298a9","tid":151270,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"姐係每次打丁 都接近無左10蚊。。<br />\n一星期打次5次就50<br />\n一年52星期就2600。。都唔小野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe888c1063651fe67b5b72a12f7711a4d326feb7","tid":151270,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔合理<br />\n點解唔去做雞呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係lor"},{"pid":"292ee7936c6ce413a8557edbc27ec9a8dee97b10","tid":151270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔合理<br />\n點解唔去做雞呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係lor</blockquote><br />\n會窮"},{"pid":"5def00f0b278394ba6c8957066f0f939105d0782","tid":151270,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"250ml 即係一包檸檬茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要打幾耐先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaf7721aa2deb596c5da98cf607bac7ffafae6c","tid":151270,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔合理<br />\n點解唔去做雞呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係lor</blockquote><br />\n會窮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同啲雞買，轉賣賺差價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696259c492035ef75f387abe2fa1a080e2ce3dd9","tid":151270,"uid":44057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T19:00:37.000Z","msg":"20歲 男教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb8d710cdff498e6859642c1aa460d05294d8e2","tid":15127